name: Tran and Partners
overview:
Based in Atlanta, GA, Tran & Partners focuses on providing small business with creative, strategically and data-driven marketing solutions to increase sales, promote awareness and sustain a competitive advantage in the marketplace. We do this by developing creative campaign strategies, consistent branding, and utilization of online technology to support our clients marketing and related functions.

Our areas of expertise include but are not limited to strategic planning, branding development, direct mail, email, website development, search engine optimization (SEO), and social media marketing.

Our goal is to improve our client’s customers retention and acquisition, attract potential customers, create strong branding, differentiate against competition, increase community awareness, and generate an overall high customer base.
